DATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Übersicht","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Gibt ein Duplikat des Knotens, auf dem diese Methode aufgerufen wurde, zurück.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <var>dupNode</var> = <var>node</var>.cloneNode(<var>deep</var>);\n</pre>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"node\"><code>node</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Knoten, welcher dupliziert werden soll.</dd>\n <dt id=\"dupnode\"><code>dupNode</code></dt>\n <dd>Der duplizierte Knoten.</dd>\n <dt id=\"deep\"><code>deep</code></dt>\n <dd><code>true</code> wenn die Kindknoten des Knotens ebenfalls dupliziert werden sollen, <code>false</code> wenn nur der Knoten dupliziert werden soll.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Hinweis:</strong> In der DOM4 Spezifikation (implementiert in Gecko&nbsp;13.0 (Firefox 13 / Thunderbird 13 / SeaMonkey 2.10)), ist das Argument <code>deep</code> optional. Es ist dann laut Spezifikation <strong><code>true</code></strong>.</p>\n\n<p>Leider wurde dies in der letzten Spezifikation geändert, sodass der Standardwert nun <strong><code>false</code></strong> ist. Auch wenn es immer noch optional ist, sollte man das Argument <code>deep</code> aus diesen Kompatibilitätsgründen setzen. Ab Gecko&nbsp;28.0 (Firefox 28 / Thunderbird 28 / SeaMonkey 2.25 / Firefox OS 1.3) warnt die Konsole den Entwickler, wenn das Argument nicht gesetzt ist.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"para1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p_prime <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">cloneNode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Hinweise","isH3":false,"content":"<p id=\"not-event-listeners\">Der duplizierte Knoten enthält alle Attribute und deren Werte, aber nicht die Eventlistener welche via <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/element.addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a> oder über die jeweilige Elementeigenschaft (z.B. <code>node.onclick = function</code>) gesetzt wurden. Im Fall eines <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code>-Elements wird das gezeichnete Bild <em>nicht</em> mitkopiert.</p>\n\n<p>Der mit <code>cloneNode()</code> duplizierte Knoten ist noch nicht Teil des Dokuments und hat keinen Elternknoten bis er mithilfe der Methode <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>Node.appendChild()</code></a> oder einer anderen vergleichbaren Methode in das Dokument eingefügt wird.</p>\n\n<p>Wenn <code>deep</code> auf <code>false</code> gesetzt ist, werden die Kindknoten nicht mitkopiert. Dies schließt ebenfalls alle Textelemente mit ein, da diese in einem oder mehreren Kindknoten enthalten sind.</p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect3\"><strong>Warnung:</strong>&nbsp;Die Verwendung von&nbsp;<code>cloneNode()</code> kann dazu führen, dass&nbsp;die selbe ID im Dokument mehrmals existiert.</div>\n\n<p>Wenn der Originalknoten eine ID hat, sollte diese im dupliziertem Knoten geändert oder gelöscht werden, um Probleme zu vermeiden. Dies sollte auch für das <code>name</code> Attribut überlegt werden.</p>\n\n<p>Um einen Knoten aus einem anderen Dokument zu kopieren sollte die <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/importNode\"><code>Document.importNode()</code></a> verwendet werden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompatibilität","title":"Browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect4\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect5\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect6\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>deep</code> as an optional parameter</td>\n   <td>\n    <p>Ja</p>\n\n    <p>(Standard: <code>false</code>)</p>\n   </td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/13\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2012-06-05.\">13.0</a> (13.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>Yes</p>\n\n    <p>(default is <code>false</code>)</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome für Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>deep</code> as an optional parameter</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>13.0 (13.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-3A0ED0A4\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: cloneNode</a><span title=\"Recommendation\" style=\"color:#fff;background:#309c40;display:inline-block; font-size:x-small; margin-left:6px; white-space:nowrap; padding:2px 5px;\">REC</span></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Core/core.html#ID-3A0ED0A4\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 3 Core: cloneNode</a><span title=\"Recommendation\" style=\"color:#fff;background:#309c40;display:inline-block; font-size:x-small; margin-left:6px; white-space:nowrap; padding:2px 5px;\">REC</span></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://dvcs.w3.org/hg/domcore/raw-file/tip/Overview.html#dom-node-clonenode\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM4: cloneNode</a> (draft)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Übersicht","id":"summary"},{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"example"},{"text":"Hinweise","id":"notes"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"}],"summary":"Gibt ein Duplikat des Knotens, auf dem diese Methode aufgerufen wurde, zurück.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.cloneNode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element.cloneNode","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Node.cloneNode()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/node/clonenode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/node/clonenode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode","title":"Node.cloneNode"}],"pageTitle":"Node.cloneNode - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}